title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
description: When accessing the Show Report Parameters dialog, the default values are not displayed.
OB: When previewing the report and clicking the Show Report Parameters button, the default values are not shown in the value box for the parameters.
EB: The expected result is that the default values should be displayed in the value box, allowing me to modify the parameters I want to change.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Preview the report
2. Click the Show Report Parameters button

Expected result: The default values should be shown in the value box for each parameter
Actual result: In the Enter Parameters dialog, all values are empty, which requires manually inputting all values even though I only wanted to modify one parameter.
